## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="ac3de-179">Если <xref:System.Data.ParameterDirection> выводится и выполнение связанного <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> не возвращает значение, <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleParameter> содержит значение null.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3de-179">If the <xref:System.Data.ParameterDirection> is output, and execution of the associated <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> does not return a value, the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleParameter> contains a null value.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="ac3de-180">Параметры `Output`, `InputOut`и `ReturnValue`, возвращаемые вызывающими <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand.ExecuteReader%2A>, недоступны до тех пор, пока не будет вызвана <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader.Close%2A> в <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3de-180">`Output`, `InputOut`, and `ReturnValue` parameters returned by calling <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand.ExecuteReader%2A> cannot be accessed until you call <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader.Close%2A> on the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader>.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="ac3de-181">В следующем примере создается <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleParameter> и задаются некоторые его свойства.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac3de-181">The following example creates a <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleParameter> and sets some of its properties.</span></span>  
  
```vb  
Public Sub CreateOracleDbParameter()  
   Dim parameter As New OracleParameter()  
   parameter.ParameterName = "pDName"  
   parameter.DbType = DbType.String  
   parameter.Value = "ENGINEERING"  
   parameter.SourceColumn = "DName"  
End Sub  
```  
  
```csharp  
public void CreateOracleDbParameter()   
{  
   OracleParameter parameter = new OracleParameter();  
   parameter.ParameterName = "pDName";  
   parameter.DbType = DbType.String;  
   parameter.Value = "ENGINEERING";  
   parameter.SourceColumn = "DName";  
}  
```

  
  
